data.description: Double wide manufactured property located on a peaceful 4 acre private lot with panoramic Tucson Mountain views from all directions. This property is zoned for horses. There are 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and 2 living rooms, fireplace & let's not forget the detached garage, shed and Solar Panels! Featuring ample space to host or raise a family. Come check it out!
